'''傑瑞米·-{zh-cn:迪克森;zh-hk:迪金遜;zh-tw:狄克遜}-·派克斯曼'''（'''Jeremy Dickson Paxman'''<ref name = WW>{{cite book|contribution=PAXMAN, Jeremy Dickson|contribution-url=http://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/article/oupww/whoswho/U30303|title=[[Who's_Who_(UK)|Who's Who 2009]]|edition=Online|location=Oxford|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|date=December 2008|accessdate=19 April 2009|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618012101/https://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/10.1093/ww/9780199540884.001.0001/ww-9780199540884-e-30303;jsessionid=D955ACA391B831F1B88D7B00CCFF08D6|dead-url=no}}{{Subscription or membership required}}</ref><ref name="Independent: Outsider">{{Cite news|first=Ian|last=Burrell|title=Jeremy Paxman: The outsider|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/jeremy-paxman-the-outsider-462914.html|newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=25 August 2007|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204231023/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/profiles/jeremy-paxman-the-outsider-462914.html|archivedate=2009年2月4日|accessdate=15 April 2013|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，{{bd|1950年|5月11日}}），英國[[主持人|廣播員]]、[[新聞從業員|新聞工作者]]與作家。派克斯曼自1972年以來，長期服務於[[英国广播公司|BBC]]，以其特別針對政客直率、火爆的訪談風格著稱。他定期出現在BBC第二台的《[[新聞之夜|新聞之夜]]》節目，評價正反兩極，評論攻擊其咄咄逼人、具恐嚇性且屈尊俯就，亦有對其堅毅且敏銳風格的正面褒揚<ref>{{cite news |last=Mosey |first=Roger |title=BBC and the 'Paxman Problem' |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/newswatch/ukfs/hi/newsid_4460000/newsid_4463800/4463837.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=20 April 2005 |accessdate=15 April 2013 |archive-date=2012-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221054405/http://news.bbc.co.uk/newswatch/ukfs/hi/newsid_4460000/newsid_4463800/4463837.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他是英國老牌智力競賽節目《{{tsl|en|University Challenge|大学挑战赛}}》的解題高手，於1994年節目改版時，接替{{tsl|en|Bamber Gascoigne|班巴·盖斯科恩}}的職位。

2014年四月底，派克斯曼宣布自己將在六月離開主持了25年的《新聞之夜》<ref name="Petersen">Hannah Ellis-Petersen [http://www.theguardian.com/media/2014/apr/30/jeremy-paxman-quit-newsnight-bbc "Jeremy Paxman to quit Newsnight after 25 years"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theguardian.com/media/2014/apr/30/jeremy-paxman-quit-newsnight-bbc |date=20201112014514 }}, theguardian.com, 30 April 2014</ref>。

